            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Gezo">Gitio</name></persName> filio bone
                        memorie <persName><name ref="Pipinus">Pipini</name></persName> offre pro
                        anima in <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> et <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Landed_possessions #Wine #Churches #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/126">Sancti Bartholomei</orgName> apostoli qui
                        ponitur <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/281">Sestinge Curte
                            Maymberti</placeName>, idest una <rs key="#Petiae">petia</rs> de terra
                        quod <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs> est posita in loco ubi dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Wine" ref="#places/311"
                            >Fullona</placeName>, qui uno capo cum uno lato [tenet] in vinea de
                            <orgName key="#Confinia #Petiae #Wine" ref="#juridical_persons/126"
                            >supracripto monasterio</orgName>, altero capo tenet in via publica, et
                        uno lato tenet in <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Petiae #Wine"><name ref="Morectus"
                            >Moreti</name></persName> filio bone memorie <persName><name
                                ref="Gherardus">Girardi</name></persName>, con tutte le sue
                        dipendenze. Chiede a <persName key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"><name
                                ref="Romanus">Romanus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> donni
                        imperatoris la stesura della cartula. Actum <placeName ref="#places/281"
                            >Sestinge</placeName>. Testimoni: <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Pepo">Pepi</name></persName> filii bone memorie <persName><name
                                ref="Raterius">Raiteri</name></persName>; <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Rustichellus">Rustichelli</name></persName> germani sui;
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Corbulus">Corbuli</name></persName>
                        filii bone memorie <persName><name ref="Martinus">Martini</name></persName>.
                        Scrive: Romanus notarius et iudex donni imperatoris.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
